author: wddgit
body:
#### PR description:

This is part of a Core campaign to eliminate all references to legacy type modules from CMSSW.

This deletes the test module dumpDTDigi.cc. Some reasons:
* Broken since at least 2015 (no consumes, it would throw)
* Not compiled currently (would fail compilation since January 2023 because it's legacy)
* Last edited in 2006
* Content looks useless ( bunch of asserts)

#### PR validation:

None. Only deletes an unused file.
title: Delete last simulation legacy type module
